OL,3,CThree dead in suspected virus outbreak
OL,4,Con cruise ship in Atlantic Ocean
OL,6,FThree people have died in a suspected
OL,7,Foutbreak of hantavirus on a cruise
OL,8,Fship in the Atlantic Ocean, the World
OL,9,FHealth Organisation (WHO) has said.
OL,11,FThe WHO said one case of hantavirus
OL,12,Finfection has been confirmed, and
OL,13,Fthere are five additional suspected
OL,14,Fcases.
OL,16,FOne of those affected is currently in
OL,17,Fintensive care in South Africa.
OL,19,FThe suspected outbreak was reported on
OL,20,Fthe MV Hondius, which was travelling
OL,21,Fbetween Argentina and Cape Verde.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
