OL,3,CThree dead in suspected virus outbreak
OL,4,Con cruise ship in Atlantic Ocean
OL,6,FHantaviruses are mainly spread by
OL,7,Frodents, particularly through exposure
OL,8,Fto infected rodents' urine or faeces.
OL,10,FBut, while rare, it may spread between
OL,11,Fpeople and can lead to "severe
OL,12,Frespiratory illness".
OL,14,FSouth African media have reported that
OL,15,Fhealth department spokesperson, Foster
OL,16,FMohale, said the first victim was an
OL,17,Felderly man.
OL,19,FHis wife later died in a South African
OL,20,Fhospital, Mohale said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
