OL,3,CThree dead in suspected virus outbreak
OL,4,Con cruise ship in Atlantic Ocean
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the WHO confirmed it
OL,12,Fis "supporting a public health event
OL,13,Finvolving a cruise vessel sailing in
OL,14,Fthe Atlantic Ocean."
OL,16,FIt continued: "Detailed investigations
OL,17,Fare ongoing, including further
OL,18,Flaboratory testing, and
OL,19,Fepidemiological investigations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
