OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777978995
OL,3,CThree dead in suspected virus outbreak
OL,4,Con cruise ship in Atlantic Ocean
OL,6,F"Medical care and support are being
OL,7,Fprovided to passengers and crew.
OL,8,FSequencing of the virus is also
OL,9,Fongoing."
OL,11,F"WHO is facilitating coordination
OL,12,Fbetween Member States and the Ship's
OL,13,Foperators for medical evacuation of
OL,14,Ftwo symptomatic passengers, as well as
OL,15,Ffull public health risk assessment and
OL,16,Fsupport to the remaining passengers on
OL,17,Fboard," the statement added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
