OL,3,CThree dead in suspected virus outbreak
OL,4,Con cruise ship in Atlantic Ocean
OL,6,FThe MarineTraffic global shipping
OL,7,Fwebsite identified the vessel as a
OL,8,FDutch-flagged passenger cruise ship.
OL,9,FIt was located docked in Praia, the
OL,10,Fcapital of Cape Verde, on Sunday night.
OL,12,FA Foreign Office spokesperson said:
OL,13,F"We are closely monitoring reports of
OL,14,Fa potential hantavirus outbreak on the
OL,15,Fcruise ship Hondius and stand ready to
OL,16,Fsupport British nationals if needed.
OL,18,F"We are in touch with the cruise
OL,19,Fcompany and local authorities."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
